            "answer_text": "I host my website on Blogger, it will shut down.People on other platforms who depend on Google traffic, will lose that.YouTubers will be red because of lost revenue.People might lose their ways because of no Google maps.Android devices will not be able to function well.Google Chrome browser might not also work, and all my passwords are stored there.Google AdSense will also shut down, which means loss of revenue.Google AdWords will shut too, which means more loss of revenue.Twitter will be on fire, everyone asking when it\u2019s going to be back.Their competitors will try to tap into the advantage, hoping they never return.In general, this world will feel it so very well if Google shuts down for a while! I pray it never happens. ",
